title: Designs for Citibank/Citicorp Logos
medium: Black marker and graphite on white tracing paper
description: Vertical list of four Citibank/Citicorp logotype designs. Top two designs use bold slab-serif font with second design rendered in caps. Bottom two designs use thin sans-serif font. Each logotype is paired with logo depicting four-pointed star within black horizontal oval. Onfirst design, logo is placed directly below logotype, left. On bottom three designs, logo is placed alongside logotype, right.
name: Drawing
